{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":1527,"text":"Something happened in the early morning hours"},{"time":4315,"text":"of May 2nd, 2000, that had a profound effect"},{"time":7900,"text":"on the way our society operates."},{"time":10206,"text":"Ironically, hardly anyone noticed at the time."},{"time":13484,"text":"The change was silent, imperceptible,"},{"time":16144,"text":"unless you knew exactly what to look for."},{"time":18989,"text":"On that morning, U.S. President Bill Clinton"},{"time":21340,"text":"ordered that a special switch be thrown"},{"time":23612,"text":"in the orbiting satellites of the Global Positioning System."},{"time":27045,"text":"Instantaneously, every civilian GPS receiver"},{"time":30909,"text":"around the globe went from errors the size of a football field"},{"time":35471,"text":"to errors the size of a small room."}]},{"cues":[{"time":42314,"text":"It's hard to overstate the effect that this change"},{"time":46105,"text":"in accuracy has had on us."},{"time":48657,"text":"Before this switch was thrown, we didn't have"},{"time":50904,"text":"in-car navigation systems giving turn-by-turn"},{"time":53163,"text":"directions, because back then, GPS couldn't tell you"},{"time":55755,"text":"what block you were on, let alone what street."}]},{"cues":[{"time":58449,"text":"For geolocation, accuracy matters,"},{"time":61697,"text":"and things have only improved over the last 10 years."},{"time":64955,"text":"With more base stations, more ground stations,"},{"time":67074,"text":"better receivers and better algorithms,"},{"time":70043,"text":"GPS can now not only tell you what street you are on,"},{"time":73106,"text":"but what part of the street."}]},{"cues":[{"time":77608,"text":"This level of accuracy"},{"time":79854,"text":"has unleashed a firestorm of innovation."},{"time":82780,"text":"In fact, many of you navigated here today"},{"time":85451,"text":"with the help of your TomTom or your smartphone."},{"time":89044,"text":"Paper maps are becoming obsolete."}]},{"cues":[{"time":92269,"text":"But we now stand on the verge of another revolution"},{"time":96408,"text":"in geolocation accuracy."},{"time":98403,"text":"What if I told you that the two-meter positioning"},{"time":101136,"text":"that our current cell phones and our TomToms give us"},{"time":104567,"text":"is pathetic compared to what we could be getting?"},{"time":108464,"text":"For some time now, it's been known that if you pay attention"},{"time":111297,"text":"to the carrier phase of the GPS signal,"},{"time":113832,"text":"and if you have an Internet connection,"},{"time":116313,"text":"then you can go from meter level to centimeter level,"},{"time":119129,"text":"even millimeter-level positioning."}]},{"cues":[{"time":122096,"text":"So why don't we have this capability on our phones?"},{"time":125376,"text":"Only, I believe, for a lack of imagination."},{"time":129746,"text":"Manufacturers haven't built this carrier phase technique"},{"time":132913,"text":"into their cheap GPS chips"},{"time":135019,"text":"because they're not sure what the general public would do"},{"time":137173,"text":"with geolocation so accurate that you could pinpoint"},{"time":140749,"text":"the wrinkles in the palm of your hand."},{"time":144587,"text":"But you and I and other innovators,"},{"time":146974,"text":"we can see the potential in this next leap in accuracy."},{"time":151014,"text":"Imagine, for example, an augmented reality app"},{"time":153726,"text":"that overlays a virtual world to millimeter-level precision"},{"time":157263,"text":"on top of the physical world."},{"time":159271,"text":"I could build for you a structure up here in 3D,"},{"time":162158,"text":"millimeter accurate, that only you could see,"},{"time":164526,"text":"or my friends at home."}]},{"cues":[{"time":167419,"text":"So this level of positioning, this is what we're looking for,"},{"time":171934,"text":"and I believe that, within the next few years, I predict,"},{"time":175858,"text":"that this kind of hyper-precise, carrier phase-based positioning"},{"time":180841,"text":"will become cheap and ubiquitous,"},{"time":184065,"text":"and the consequences will be fantastic."}]},{"cues":[{"time":186610,"text":"The Holy Grail, of course, is the GPS dot."},{"time":191266,"text":"Do you remember the movie \"The Da Vinci Code?\""},{"time":193946,"text":"Here's Professor Langdon examining a GPS dot,"},{"time":197394,"text":"which his accomplice tells him is a tracking device"},{"time":200771,"text":"accurate within two feet anywhere on the globe,"},{"time":203832,"text":"but we know that in the world of nonfiction,"},{"time":206738,"text":"the GPS dot is impossible, right?"},{"time":209602,"text":"For one thing, GPS doesn't work indoors,"},{"time":212226,"text":"and for another, they don't make devices quite this small,"},{"time":215410,"text":"especially when those devices have to relay"},{"time":217738,"text":"their measurements back over a network."}]},{"cues":[{"time":220713,"text":"Well, these objections were perfectly reasonable"},{"time":223051,"text":"a few years ago, but things have changed."},{"time":226065,"text":"There's been a strong trend toward miniaturization,"},{"time":228921,"text":"better sensitivity, so much so that, a few years ago,"},{"time":232640,"text":"a GPS tracking device looked like this clunky box"},{"time":235344,"text":"to the left of the keys."},{"time":237520,"text":"Compare that with the device released just months ago"},{"time":240171,"text":"that's now packaged into something the size of a key fob,"},{"time":243963,"text":"and if you take a look at the state of the art"},{"time":246516,"text":"for a complete GPS receiver, which is only a centimeter"},{"time":249262,"text":"on a side and more sensitive than ever,"},{"time":251349,"text":"you realize that the GPS dot will soon move"},{"time":254858,"text":"from fiction to nonfiction."}]},{"cues":[{"time":259257,"text":"Imagine what we could do with a world full of GPS dots."},{"time":263499,"text":"It's not just that you'll never lose your wallet or your keys"},{"time":266405,"text":"anymore, or your child when you're at Disneyland."},{"time":270976,"text":"You'll buy GPS dots in bulk, and you'll stick them on"},{"time":274757,"text":"everything you own worth more than a few tens of dollars."}]},{"cues":[{"time":278724,"text":"I couldn't find my shoes one recent morning,"},{"time":281196,"text":"and, as usual, had to ask my wife if she had seen them."},{"time":284564,"text":"But I shouldn't have to bother my wife with that kind of triviality."},{"time":288356,"text":"I should be able to ask my house where my shoes are."},{"time":290967,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":293106,"text":"Those of you who have made the switch to Gmail,"},{"time":296614,"text":"remember how refreshing it was to go from"},{"time":299492,"text":"organizing all of your email to simply searching it."},{"time":303636,"text":"The GPS dot will do the same for our possessions."}]},{"cues":[{"time":308138,"text":"Now, of course, there is a flip side to the GPS dot."},{"time":312824,"text":"I was in my office some months back"},{"time":315213,"text":"and got a telephone call."},{"time":317756,"text":"The woman on the other end of the line, we'll call her Carol,"},{"time":321377,"text":"was panicked."},{"time":323456,"text":"Apparently, an ex-boyfriend of Carol's from California"},{"time":326249,"text":"had found her in Texas and was following her around."},{"time":329564,"text":"So you might ask at this point why she's calling you."},{"time":333401,"text":"Well, so did I."},{"time":334800,"text":"But it turned out there was a technical twist to Carol's case."},{"time":338791,"text":"Every time her ex-boyfriend would show up,"},{"time":341525,"text":"at the most improbable times and the most improbable locations,"},{"time":345875,"text":"he was carrying an open laptop,"},{"time":348571,"text":"and over time Carol realized that he had planted"},{"time":351414,"text":"a GPS tracking device on her car,"},{"time":353962,"text":"so she was calling me for help to disable it."}]},{"cues":[{"time":356871,"text":"\"Well, you should go to a good mechanic"},{"time":358859,"text":"and have him look at your car,\" I said."}]},{"cues":[{"time":362143,"text":"\"I already have,\" she told me."},{"time":364847,"text":"\"He didn't see anything obvious,"},{"time":366991,"text":"and he said he'd have to take the car apart piece by piece.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":370528,"text":"\"Well then, you'd better go to the police,\" I said."}]},{"cues":[{"time":373849,"text":"\"I already have,\" she replied."},{"time":376953,"text":"\"They're not sure this rises to the level of harassment,"},{"time":379399,"text":"and they're not set up technically to find the device.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":383152,"text":"\"Okay, what about the FBI?\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":384658,"text":"\"I've talked to them too, and same story.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":388821,"text":"We then talked about her coming to my lab"},{"time":390491,"text":"and us performing a radio sweep of her car,"},{"time":393039,"text":"but I wasn't even sure that would work,"},{"time":395538,"text":"given that some of these devices are configured"},{"time":397589,"text":"to only transmit when they're inside safe zones"},{"time":399823,"text":"or when the car is moving."}]},{"cues":[{"time":403127,"text":"So, there we were."},{"time":404621,"text":"Carol isn't the first, and certainly won't be the last,"},{"time":407590,"text":"to find herself in this kind of fearsome environment,"},{"time":412525,"text":"worrisome situation caused by GPS tracking."}]},{"cues":[{"time":418410,"text":"In fact, as I looked into her case,"},{"time":420213,"text":"I discovered to my surprise that it's not clearly illegal"},{"time":423675,"text":"for you or me to put a tracking device on someone else's car."},{"time":428108,"text":"The Supreme Court ruled last month that a policeman"},{"time":431988,"text":"has to get a warrant if he wants to do prolonged tracking,"},{"time":436320,"text":"but the law isn't clear about civilians doing this to one another,"},{"time":439836,"text":"so it's not just Big Brother we have to worry about,"},{"time":442466,"text":"but Big Neighbor. (Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":445737,"text":"There is one alternative that Carol could have taken,"},{"time":450385,"text":"very effective. It's called the Wave Bubble."},{"time":456088,"text":"It's an open-source GPS jammer,"},{"time":459023,"text":"developed by Limor Fried,"},{"time":461578,"text":"a graduate student at MIT, and Limor calls it"},{"time":465371,"text":"\"a tool for reclaiming our personal space.\""},{"time":469256,"text":"With a flip of the switch you create a bubble around you"},{"time":471521,"text":"within which GPS signals can't reside."},{"time":473768,"text":"They get drowned out by the bubble."},{"time":476124,"text":"And Limor designed this, in part, because, like Carol,"},{"time":479771,"text":"she felt threatened by GPS tracking."},{"time":482417,"text":"Then she posted her design to the web,"},{"time":484993,"text":"and if you don't have time to build your own,"},{"time":488735,"text":"you can buy one."},{"time":489509,"text":"Chinese manufacturers now sell thousands"},{"time":491567,"text":"of nearly identical devices on the Internet."}]},{"cues":[{"time":495340,"text":"So you might be thinking, the Wave Bubble sounds great."},{"time":499492,"text":"I should have one. Might come in handy if somebody ever puts a tracking device on my car."},{"time":503145,"text":"But you should be aware that its use is very much illegal"},{"time":506927,"text":"in the United States."},{"time":508726,"text":"And why is that?"},{"time":509473,"text":"Well, because it's not a bubble at all."},{"time":512566,"text":"Its jamming signals don't stop at the edge"},{"time":514965,"text":"of your personal space or at the edge of your car."},{"time":517437,"text":"They go on to jam innocent GPS receivers for miles around you. (Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":523673,"text":"Now, if you're Carol or Limor,"},{"time":526424,"text":"or someone who feels threatened by GPS tracking,"},{"time":529049,"text":"it might not feel wrong to turn on a Wave Bubble,"},{"time":532824,"text":"but in fact, the results can be disastrous."},{"time":536804,"text":"Imagine, for example, you're the captain of a cruise ship"},{"time":539524,"text":"trying to make your way through a thick fog"},{"time":542043,"text":"and some passenger in the back turns on a Wave Bubble."},{"time":545883,"text":"All of a sudden your GPS readout goes blank,"},{"time":548598,"text":"and now it's just you and the fog"},{"time":551884,"text":"and whatever you can pull off the radar system"},{"time":554484,"text":"if you remember how to work it."},{"time":557608,"text":"They -- in fact, they don't update or upkeep lighthouses"},{"time":563544,"text":"anymore, and LORAN, the only backup to GPS,"},{"time":568197,"text":"was discontinued last year."}]},{"cues":[{"time":570617,"text":"Our modern society has a special relationship with GPS."},{"time":575530,"text":"We're almost blindly reliant on it."},{"time":577800,"text":"It's built deeply into our systems and infrastructure."},{"time":581451,"text":"Some call it \"the invisible utility.\""},{"time":585079,"text":"So, turning on a Wave Bubble might not just cause inconvenience."},{"time":588801,"text":"It might be deadly."}]},{"cues":[{"time":593171,"text":"But as it turns out, for purposes of protecting your privacy"},{"time":597379,"text":"at the expense of general GPS reliability,"},{"time":600868,"text":"there's something even more potent"},{"time":603028,"text":"and more subversive than a Wave Bubble,"},{"time":606820,"text":"and that is a GPS spoofer."}]},{"cues":[{"time":610209,"text":"The idea behind the GPS spoofer is simple."},{"time":613034,"text":"Instead of jamming the GPS signals, you fake them."},{"time":617011,"text":"You imitate them, and if you do it right, the device"},{"time":620129,"text":"you're attacking doesn't even know it's being spoofed."}]},{"cues":[{"time":623296,"text":"So let me show you how this works."},{"time":624928,"text":"In any GPS receiver, there's a peak inside"},{"time":627653,"text":"that corresponds to the authentic signals."},{"time":630288,"text":"These three red dots represent the tracking points"},{"time":633103,"text":"that try to keep themselves centered on that peak."},{"time":635982,"text":"But if you send in a fake GPS signal,"},{"time":639047,"text":"another peak pops up, and if you can get these two peaks"},{"time":643513,"text":"perfectly aligned, the tracking points can't tell the difference,"},{"time":648231,"text":"and they get hijacked by the stronger counterfeit signal,"},{"time":651542,"text":"with the authentic peak getting forced off."},{"time":655502,"text":"At this point, the game is over."},{"time":657669,"text":"The fake signals now completely control this GPS receiver."}]},{"cues":[{"time":661406,"text":"So is this really possible?"},{"time":662901,"text":"Can someone really manipulate"},{"time":664624,"text":"the timing and positioning of a GPS receiver"},{"time":666606,"text":"just like that, with a spoofer?"},{"time":669485,"text":"Well, the short answer is yes."},{"time":671500,"text":"The key is that civil GPS signals"},{"time":674304,"text":"are completely open."},{"time":675406,"text":"They have no encryption. They have no authentication."},{"time":679397,"text":"They're wide open, vulnerable to a kind of spoofing attack."},{"time":682892,"text":"Even so, up until very recently,"},{"time":685467,"text":"nobody worried about GPS spoofers."},{"time":687859,"text":"People figured that it would be too complex"},{"time":689837,"text":"or too expensive for some hacker to build one."}]},{"cues":[{"time":692652,"text":"But I, and a friend of mine from graduate school,"},{"time":696604,"text":"we didn't see it that way."},{"time":698756,"text":"We knew it wasn't going to be so hard,"},{"time":701229,"text":"and we wanted to be the first to build one"},{"time":703157,"text":"so we could get out in front of the problem"},{"time":705237,"text":"and help protect against GPS spoofing."},{"time":709343,"text":"I remember vividly the week it all came together."},{"time":712688,"text":"We built it at my home, which means that"},{"time":716137,"text":"I got a little extra help from my three-year-old son Ramon."},{"time":720526,"text":"Here's Ramon — (Laughter) —"},{"time":722944,"text":"looking for a little attention from Dad that week."},{"time":726629,"text":"At first, the spoofer was just a jumble of cables"},{"time":728899,"text":"and computers, though we eventually got it packaged"},{"time":731781,"text":"into a small box."}]},{"cues":[{"time":733453,"text":"Now, the Dr. Frankenstein moment,"},{"time":736262,"text":"when the spoofer finally came alive"},{"time":738989,"text":"and I glimpsed its awful potential,"},{"time":741590,"text":"came late one night when I tested the spoofer"},{"time":744326,"text":"against my iPhone."},{"time":746412,"text":"Let me show you some actual footage from that"},{"time":748029,"text":"very first experiment."},{"time":749965,"text":"I had come to completely trust this little blue dot"},{"time":753559,"text":"and its reassuring blue halo."},{"time":755194,"text":"They seemed to speak to me."},{"time":756269,"text":"They'd say, \"Here you are. Here you are.\" (Laughter)"},{"time":760929,"text":"And \"you can trust us.\""},{"time":763799,"text":"So something felt very wrong about the world."},{"time":768917,"text":"It was a sense, almost, of betrayal,"},{"time":771500,"text":"when this little blue dot started at my house,"},{"time":775691,"text":"and went running off toward the north"},{"time":777303,"text":"leaving me behind. I wasn't moving."},{"time":781198,"text":"What I then saw in this little moving blue dot"},{"time":785431,"text":"was the potential for chaos."},{"time":788149,"text":"I saw airplanes and ships veering off course, with the captain"},{"time":792291,"text":"learning only too late that something was wrong."},{"time":796565,"text":"I saw the GPS-derived timing"},{"time":799065,"text":"of the New York Stock Exchange"},{"time":800796,"text":"being manipulated by hackers."},{"time":802746,"text":"You can scarcely imagine the kind of havoc"},{"time":805714,"text":"you could cause if you knew what you were doing"},{"time":808364,"text":"with a GPS spoofer."}]},{"cues":[{"time":811717,"text":"There is, though, one redeeming feature"},{"time":816861,"text":"of the GPS spoofer."},{"time":819317,"text":"It's the ultimate weapon against an invasion of GPS dots."},{"time":823918,"text":"Imagine, for example, you're being tracked."},{"time":827005,"text":"Well, you can play the tracker for a fool,"},{"time":829529,"text":"pretending to be at work when you're really on vacation."},{"time":832490,"text":"Or, if you're Carol, you could lure your ex-boyfriend"},{"time":835205,"text":"into some empty parking lot"},{"time":836522,"text":"where the police are waiting for him."}]},{"cues":[{"time":838823,"text":"So I'm fascinated by this conflict, a looming conflict,"},{"time":844026,"text":"between privacy on the one hand"},{"time":846691,"text":"and the need for a clean radio spectrum on the other."},{"time":850890,"text":"We simply cannot tolerate GPS jammers and spoofers,"},{"time":853935,"text":"and yet, given the lack of effective legal means"},{"time":857671,"text":"for protecting our privacy from the GPS dot,"},{"time":861770,"text":"can you really blame people for wanting to turn them on,"},{"time":863642,"text":"for wanting to use them?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":866058,"text":"I hold out hope that we'll be able to reconcile"},{"time":869111,"text":"this conflict with some sort of,"},{"time":872297,"text":"some yet uninvented technology."},{"time":877727,"text":"But meanwhile, grab some popcorn,"},{"time":880853,"text":"because things are going to get interesting."}]},{"cues":[{"time":882980,"text":"Within the next few years,"},{"time":884320,"text":"many of you will be the proud owner of a GPS dot."},{"time":888574,"text":"Maybe you'll have a whole bag full of them."},{"time":890922,"text":"You'll never lose track of your things again."},{"time":894374,"text":"The GPS dot will fundamentally reorder your life."},{"time":898403,"text":"But will you be able to resist the temptation"},{"time":901085,"text":"to track your fellow man?"},{"time":904077,"text":"Or will you be able to resist the temptation"},{"time":905909,"text":"to turn on a GPS spoofer or a Wave Bubble"},{"time":909204,"text":"to protect your own privacy?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":911972,"text":"So, as usual, what we see just beyond the horizon"},{"time":915604,"text":"is full of promise and peril."},{"time":918944,"text":"It'll be fascinating to see how this all turns out."}]},{"cues":[{"time":922132,"text":"Thanks. (Applause)"}]}]}